# Optional gaming extras from the AUR — installed (via paru) only when gaming is
# enabled AND you uncomment them. Everything the CachyOS guide needs is in the
# repos (gaming.pkgs); these are just nice-to-haves that only exist on the AUR.
#
# This setup keeps AUR use to a minimum on purpose, so all entries start off.

# vkBasalt — Vulkan post-processing (CAS sharpening, FXAA, SMAA). Toggle in-game
# with the Home key. lib32 variant is needed for 32-bit / most Proton titles.
# vkbasalt
# lib32-vkbasalt

# game-devices-udev — udev rules for DualSense/DualShock/Switch Pro pads used
# OUTSIDE Steam (Steam ships its own rules). Handy for Lutris/Heroic/emulators.
# game-devices-udev
